d for the ProjectBuilder class and possibly search the Maven cache for those.", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_0b261ae36c6e8a600169fe04181b648196b5604e8c3ce52959\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp_gQ67si5MV7ZbdPXPrKDMicbKoll81u28DWko4YabvVQslkH2VKjywgRcmnc6KoMB2xC-3ZuopZjCTSy39LDkCQY_84qfUkJsm2T0qG4G9mwc_I8ugi1BqqChfQG-8IRIcQ1HTb4QTJbP-EJZeZWnlEFqNfeE8A8lwa8Tf3tf32NQ31LXotwtxtwse9eMz_NnBDurxYZhdG5KmtGCMNoEZl2pWRkBQj8V-I_Du182QN8fILGZpycHWLufdXljjxNR7lKeIeux6gRuc66GbSQCqHK0HUwJzsoMzYOIuIEpYYQv0VFo36-k75hJgupUl3_QTOlPhVgZOjjovstDeIlfUMmXhPoR9k7VWa6zVjQ5XFnyX4hx30-jOVFdsv_KErqt0LC8aDY_uDamsCVFvuW3neRCD3JwDddks2WUz-rTo0VB6UJlfTHcAAuNi5d7opBLlW9VPcf1xNm_CFC8hqkGssHZI129QVUbeuAW1jJjuzpLs5fyGjfIJmE6uR6rVdaTt6vOtLQ4zut8oTwYgCEQleTl12yGgiT0QDdqCYVyTTCuVtHxnRGaIZ8hKP_PyF-78Ahgkhoui8ANESNAAz65Um3vcF8Bg2ah0IVDj1Pu8yrgGSet9gWEw1w628YuFj0u2MljMfzDg_FgqyawZfty0w73nZJYDnqV7UEL2oa-BDpt6Dp7Q7flMNs1rkCwpZdzJ5Uw-fBo0bswOsQErRc_E7Fbk10zDm-G44Yt-3tmz-dZqsOmAN2y1ApD2fu-5d2dwHwkkqVkw_0hW6AU8ve_5AElsrUA1AMt_5KTy3PCmNoDBqgXBH-3dCxSV90yiMX23A-DWViFIWQjXVZc9dspJyrDB33D2p1JGNFNfVUca_4MwEwjVSGiwpb4-AqM0GuymQWC_pUXFwTLhxr0_0k-xSj1tGJXPT5-UQkPAnofnmLNWgrLKocOh2VzP3gPTTNJIBjEKHKCecqH59IE4bAR0d6z2asqosGaUkkL_8sAwgSx9OxKWYjb9_0rOl00noIy4bIXlFRedsb__QflFm5-qTkFgVzAVacFbrdHrXsLKicCs13haZct5OUb8PvVOWVuhZCWsLRERLNwJv-l44RJM2Hj0gfgSDxx8Pj48gA8Ywlqyg9jK2bu0QvYGgJtOgKUVZCjHkHmkwCMnkHutXQs6CUDPUOMA1d91qHFXZ9kusHJpNe9cw3kD8omB0t-HxPlz3FEZOqI9dQNr7eeiS-DPnqU7rajPGWxKVv42rkKYiTZVTUQW9kypoWF1CdkAE-XeCb6z33FDo4XzzIaFkktJ70e3eKTzDgkps4RFOHDvZLjf6gZPK92XHOUsPNaquOWDR76wuCSs5uGbCzbNoGJBH_X-DAlYWP6wNAKZjtSzwHUvtvGfg9xoLNW_x9rjH9vvGqaLRGrszRYZr7Mvu_teEwPQDahFfOTs9iWzs-jHwbbZ6rqiLzWB3E-VnoTc48B1SPJO0_QJKOsII7nSgcwj3S4UB4UdQ8weglwWCHMWZZpvRPZLioRL0oiJji4jiXJLJ6w4X4wl-nJtwQktxI2y8LcC7yR3NI-aEBmeo8JqB_ESb3Y0M4qwKWbKAKGue8bTyZtiPNRikr6KHXJoob9sKGI-vZdfMX-raMKYkxMZSDHMy9yppZgEx5ypKqs5EYKhaGYHKsoqcI4dhgprHBmOITuN73bGS1mg-MUxQ6hjwUMrZ3oE-SG2PVSq3xK4cYx7K3zlY0njpESpuV9WP_twwmgoojMaqJzJP9K-qdLDPjpuDOM